ed="T" n="0738c26"/><persName key="A009589">釋法海</persName>，字<persName key="A009589">文允</persName>，姓張氏，<placeName key="PL000000010986">丹陽</placeName>人。少出家于<placeName key="PL000000011009">鶴<lb
ed="T" n="0738c27"/>林寺</placeName>。白駒匪食其場苗<ptr target="#n847"/>，金翅<ptr target="#n617"/>俄翔其海面，<lb
ed="T" n="0738c28"/>曲從師教，周覽群經，大壑納川，鄧林聚羽<ptr target="#n848"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0738c29"/>是以圓入一性<ptr target="#n849"/>，學階<persName key="A002799">空王</persName>，擅當代獨悟之<pb ed="T" n="0739a" xml:id="T50.2061.0739a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0739a01"/>名，剖先賢不決之義，一時外學六籍<ptr target="#n32"/>該通<ptr target="#n350"/>。甞<lb
ed="T" n="0739a02"/>謂人曰：「佛法一門，極唯『心地』，餘皆椎輪<ptr target="#n850"/>也。」<date from-iso="0742" key="j19921141997410" to-iso="0756">天<lb
ed="T" n="0739a03"/>寶</date>中，預<placeName key="PL000000010783">揚州</placeName><persName key="A009590">法慎律師</persName>講肆，同<persName key="A004177">曇一</persName>、<persName key="A009591">靈一</persName>等<lb
ed="T" n="0739a04"/>推為<persName key="A002780">顏</persName>、<persName key="A009593">冉</persName>焉<ptr target="#n851"/>。復與<placeName key="PL000000012967">杼山</placeName><persName key="A008833">晝公</persName>為忘形之交，<lb
ed="T" n="0739a05"/>林下之遊。黑白二徒，多從求益焉。</p>
